<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM4.8.6">
<l>ñāla muṟṟu muṇṭu miḻnta nāta ṉeṉṟum nāṉi lañcūḻ</l>
<l>vēlai yaṉṉa kōla mēṉi vaṇṇa ṉeṉṟum mēle ḻuntu</l>
<l>cēlu kaḷum vayalkoḷ nāṅkait</l>
<l>tēva tēva ṉeṉṟeṉ ṟōti</l>
<l>pāliṉ ṉalla meṉmo ḻiyāḷ pārttaṉ paḷḷi pāṭu vāḷē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Saying, “Lord who, having eaten the entire world, disgorged it,”</l>
<l>Saying, “You, the hue of whose shapely body is of the sea</l>
<l rend="indent">which encompasses the four directions,”</l>
<l>Reciting over and over, “God of gods in Nāṅkai with paddy fields</l>
<l rend="indent">where carp leap, rising high,”</l>
<l>She, whose soft speech is as fine as milk, sings of Pārttaṉpaḷḷi.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
